{"tid":1491282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(緊急置頂!!!!)你地再咁玩Twitter就輸到仆街","createTime":"2019-08-20T11:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T02:58:17.000Z","uid":261645,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6711280a238e57feddab6aacf39bd50a215618","tid":1491282,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:09:32.000Z","msg":"我知係p 但我必需講(非分化)<br />\n<br />\n香港人終於玩twitter係好事<br />\n<br />\n但大家用twitter個陣<br />\n唔該得閒po下其他嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當自己玩ig fb咁<br />\npo下明星/貓/運動/電影/日常生活<br />\nprofile整靚佢啦</span></span><br />\n我地開Twitter唔係淨做宣傳架<br />\n我見好多新users 淨係po香港情況<br />\n咁樣比人地印象好咩！？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一陣比人當bot啊<br />\n到時我地同班5毛就冇分別架啦</span></span><br />\n記住 外國人都唔鐘意propaganda <br />\n有啲美國人都想ban俄佬fake news<br />\n我唔想過幾日Twitter 出聲ban9我地啊"},{"pid":"35b4a5e4a7c54151c01969cffcf50f07df7fe0a9","tid":1491282,"uid":110332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:10:22.000Z","msg":"之後嘅文宣重點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警察=黑社會恐怖分子，撐警=支持恐怖主義</span></span><br />\n<br />\n外國支持恐怖主義拉得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申，斬首都唔割</span></span>"},{"pid":"f8cd1eca79065c3003109a09eaa98986f86ebbb4","tid":1491282,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"e48f3131eab7615ca9e544a893d07ce0eb9d64cb","tid":1491282,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:10:47.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"ca7fd1257650d60899d595bf733fc927f57452a7","tid":1491282,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:11:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb2c2e34979ceba1dbfcab1b5ea